    "According to Halaweh (2023), ChatGPT can help students acquire research skills by offering resources and information on a particular topic, pointing out aspects that have not been explored, and introducing them to new research areas.",
    "This allows them to understand and evaluate the topic better.",
    "However, although ChatGPT provides an assistant to students in the research process, there is a growing concern about its ability to write an article or essay rather than the students themselves.",
